    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Krampus is Coming! Grab your shotgun, finish your hot punch and don't forget your mission: Save the Christmas! Big Trouble in Little Chimney is highly-addictive and fast paced arena bullet-hell shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive endless hordes of creatures lurk from the dark chimney and save the Christmas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072710/extras/a3315d12aab5c7bb43a35dc2e995d2db.apng?t=1735923294\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072710/extras/a3315d12aab5c7bb43a35dc2e995d2db.poster.avif?t=1735923294\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=64 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls and pure arcade action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick 10 minute play sessions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite replayability as you chase ever higher scores!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 10 brutal enemy types like: Turkey, Gingerbread man, or Nutcracker</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of guns for fun: Shotgun, SMG or awesome Flamethrower for all BBQ lovers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect jingle bells and gain new upgrades as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock New Weapons and special abilities in the Santa's Store</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Game modes: Krampus is coming, Giftpocalypse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handcrafted pixel graphics created with love</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great music by Kevin MacLeod</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Xbox 360 controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes Steam Achievements and small green Elves!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning</strong>: This game contains a lot of Turkeys and elements of PIXEL violence :O</p>",
